Package com.buffettinc.hrms.model.employee

Class Employee

java.lang.Object
com.buffettinc.hrms.model.employee.Employee
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Accountant, HRStaff, Manager
@Entity public class Employee extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents an Employee for Buffett Inc. Each employee has an employeeID, first name, last name, address and contact info, a hire date, department, position, and a reference to their manager, as well as PTOBalance and Payroll objects to manager PTO balances and payroll information.

2023-07-13
